Author: shnu#0359
Content: Why PIRATE coin?

Author: shnu#0359
Content:
Sorry to ask..why do we need a PIRATE coin?
Is it good to have these sub-coins for the value of KMD?

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: is it good for the ecosystem to have a coin that is much more private than XMR that is secured by bitcoin hashrate?

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: why does there have to be a direct transactional benefit for everything that is done?

Author: shnu#0359
Content: Isnt that why we have KMD?

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: KMD has a lot of transparent tx, PIRATE has none, it makes it the ultimate in privacy

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: you cant do a z->t in PIRATE

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: you can with KMD

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: so there is now more z PIRATE than any other coin out there and the anon set grows with each transaction

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: building an ecosystem is not about monetizing every last thing with some explicit lockin to KMD

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: that is not any sustainable model in an open source world

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: so the idea is to have useful projects in the ecosystem that makes the overall ecosystem better

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: now if KMD was as private as PIRATE, it would likely get delisted from exchanges

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: PIRATE is too dangerous and there is no way to know the chickens, so they would likely just ban it

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: but I am working on low cost way for people to KMD <-> PIRATE, to enable all of KMD peoples to have the benefit of PIRATE. If they choose to

Content: sorry, I dont work on some planned out roadmap

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: new ideas come to me, when they do

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: and I implement them

Content: usually a lot faster than can even be tested, let alone fully digested and marketed

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: I plan to continue to make unplanned tech developments as they spontaneously arise

Content: For anybody that believes true innovation can be planned and managed like some standard process to make a new house, I have news. It isnt.
